Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:46.19,Italics Dialogue,Aguri,0,0,0,,Còn Tasuku thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:52.49,Italics Dialogue,Aguri,0,0,0,,Yosh, viết thôi.
